'''Republic Mobile Surgical Unit 7''',<ref name="TNEGtD">''[[The New Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> also known as '''RMSU-7''' (pronounced '''Rimsoo Seven'''), was a [[Republic Mobile Surgical Unit/Legends|Republic Mobile Surgical Unit]] stationed on the jungle [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Drongar/Legends|Drongar]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] in [[20 BBY/Legends|20 BBY]].<ref name="Battle Surgeons" /> The [[Sea of Sponges]] was in between [[Republic Mobile Surgical Unit 3|RMSU-3]] and RMSU-7. It serviced the personnel of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] at the [[Battle of Drongar]] alongside other surgical units under the command of [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[D'Arc Vaetes]]. It, with all the other Republic forces on the planet, left when the [[Bota/Legends|bota]] mutated and became useless.

The medical base contained a [[Rimsoo Seven cantina|cantina]] managed by the [[Ortolan/Legends|Ortolan]], [[Baloob]].

[[Tolk le Trene]], a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Nurse/Legends|nurse]], wanted to transfer to RMSU 3 from 7 in order to be away from her lover [[Doctor/Legends|Doctor]] [[Jos Vondar]].<ref name="Jedi Healer" />

